{{Main|Wikipedia:Manual of Style/Dates and numbers#Numbers}}
*Integers from zero to nine are spelled out in words. Integers greater than nine {{em|expressible in one or two words}} may be expressed either in numerals or in words. Other numbers

{{Shortcut|MOS:COMMONMATH}}
